ygData.messageBody:
Message text written by INTERNET:warriors_eq@onelist.com
>
Oh yes I must say I forgot about that. I did the same at Misty thicket
with
my store bought bow, even if you miss you get the faction shift. Two
levels
huh? What is the real life time you spent then? aprox?

Jaade,
Indigo Sista Soldier.<

Aprox 18 hours rl time, from barely level 17 to almost level 20, with side
trips to Befallen and Najena. Lost 19 twice due to dying. Once an orc
fanatic rooted then it and three others walked over to the casters and did
them in before returning for me, the casters were unable to bring them back
to me. The shiny brass halberd (16 dam 48 delay, hits magic) was well worth
the time invested.

Oglug ~Hand of Chaos~ CT
